bhauk "=== KaleshScript Demo ==="

chutiye ye x hai 42
chutiye ye naam hai "Delhi Coder"

bhauk x
bhauk naam

bsdk agar x > 40 kar: bhauk "X bada hai!"

chutiye ye a hai 10
chutiye ye b hai 20

bsdk agar a < b kar: bhauk "a chota hai b se"

chutiye ye numbers hai [10, 20, 30]
bhauk numbers[0]
bhauk numbers[1]

chutiye ye truth hai sahi
bsdk agar truth kar: bhauk "Sahi hai!"

bhauk "Demo complete!"


